ail. Therefore, it provides a promising\nsolution for sharing genomic data with accountability requirement across\nmultiple sites.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Jul 2019 02:11:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Jul 2019 08:04:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-29"}
