o\nother 2D materials, and shall provide an improved theoretical avenue for the\naccurate analysis, modeling and design of graphene-based thermionic energy\ndevices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Jul 2019 08:46:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 30 Jul 2019 06:23:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-31"}
