pends on\nwhich directions the tides are coherent or {\\it incoherent} along, we suggest\nthat the multidimensional dependence of the substructure evolution on the tidal\ncoherence should be deeply related to the complex nature of the large-scale\nassembly bias.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Jul 2019 09:58:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-18"}
