t when GDP grows, provisions tend to fall and vice\nversa. The results also revealed other factors influencing the behavior of loan\nloss provisions, such as earning management.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Jul 2019 13:12:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-18"}
