device\nconfiguration. In order to confirm this numerical evidence, complementary\nresults from wind-tunnel experiments are presented. Finally, we describe the\nsystem behaviour when increasing further the number of devices, outlining the\nultimate goal of developing a high-performance EH network of numerous\naeroelastic energy harvesters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Jul 2019 13:14:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-23"}
