t reviewing the\nrapid progress in the field of exotic $XYZ$ hadrons over the past few years\nboth in experiments and theory. It concludes with a summary on future prospects\nand challenges.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Jul 2019 15:28:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 14 May 2020 02:25:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-19"}
