$ is a\nvector space with a totally unimodular basis matrix, to construct reduced bases\nfor the number lattice part of $V_{SP}\\leftrightarrow K_P, K_P^d,\n(V_{SP}\\leftrightarrow K_P)^d,$ from a reduced basis for the number lattice\npart of $K_P.$\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Jul 2019 07:11:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-23"}
